== Overview ==
Plasma Mines are powerful explosive charges that are placed on the ground. Because of their low hit chance they are best used with bots that have enhanced targeting AI. They are also most effective when used against large numbers of enemy units.

== Where to Acquire ==
Plasma Mines can be bought in the workshop after acquiring [[Plasma Technology]].
